org.apache.hadoop.yarn.sls.synthetic

Class SynthWorkload

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.sls.synthetic.SynthWorkload

  • public class SynthWorkload
extends Object
    This class represent a workload (made up of multiple SynthJobClass(es)). It also stores the temporal distributions of jobs in this workload.
